column2: SELECT u.up_col0 as [col0], x.objID, p.ra,p.dec,str(p.ra,#,#) as ra,str(p.[dec],#,#) as dec,p.petroMag_u,p.petroMag_g,p.petroMag_r,p.petroMag_i,p.petroMag_z,p.petroMagErr_u,p.petroMagErr_g,p.petroMagErr_r,p.petroMagErr_i,p.petroMagErr_z,p.extinction_g,p.extinction_i,p.extinction_r,p.extinction_u,p.extinction_z FROM BESTDR7.. PhotoObj AS p 	JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID          JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id  ORDER BY x.up_id
